description:
This is a 32 minute workout called '30 MIN FULL BODY WORKOUT - Apartment & Small Space Friendly (No Equipment, No Jumping)' from the channel MadFit.
The workout falls under Cardio/Mat and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: If you live in an apartment or feel limited working out at home, this workout is for you! This 30 min full body workout can be done in a small space, with NO EQUIPMENT, and there is no jumping/no noise involved.
